OL,3,CMan suffers serious injuries in attack
OL,4,Cby gang armed with bats
OL,6,FA man has suffered serious injuries
OL,7,Fafter he was assaulted by a masked
OL,8,Fgang armed with bats in Co Antrim.
OL,10,FDetectives are appealing for
OL,11,Finformation and witnesses following
OL,12,Fthe incident in Ballyclare on Sunday.
OL,14,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "At
OL,15,Fapproximately 12.40am this morning,
OL,16,FSunday 12th July, we received a report
OL,17,Fthat a man had been assaulted outside
OL,18,Fa property in the Thornhill Drive area
OL,19,Fof the town.
