PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783957707
OL,3,CMan suffers serious injuries in attack
OL,4,Cby gang armed with bats
OL,6,F"It's understood that the man, aged in
OL,7,Fhis 30s, was assaulted by up to eight
OL,8,Fmasked men armed with bats.
OL,10,F"The victim was taken to hospital for
OL,11,Ftreatment to serious injuries caused
OL,12,Fto his leg, head, wrist and arms.
OL,14,F"Those responsible for this attack
OL,15,Fhave shown a complete disregard for
OL,16,Fhuman dignity and the rule of the law."
OL,18,FThe victim has been left with lasting
OL,19,Fphysical and psychological trauma,
OL,20,Fpolice said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUxD@gO]
