PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783957707
OL,3,CMan suffers serious injuries in attack
OL,4,Cby gang armed with bats
OL,6,FThe spokesperson added: "No one
OL,7,Fdeserves to be attacked in this way.
OL,8,FThere is no justification for this
OL,9,Fviolence.
OL,11,F"Anyone who witnessed what happened or
OL,12,Fhas information that could help with
OL,13,Four enquiries is asked to contact
OL,14,Fpolice on 101, quoting reference
OL,15,Fnumber 64 12/07/26."
